<section>
    <h2>Current Offers</h2>

    <article class="resource-card">
        <h3>Urban Farming Toolkit and Training</h3>
        <p><strong>Offered by:</strong> Center for Civic Participation (C4C)</p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Bengaluru (available for other communities)</p>

        <h4>What's Included</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Plant selection guide for local climate</li>
            <li>Soil preparation instructions</li>
            <li>Irrigation system setup guide</li>
            <li>Maintenance schedules</li>
            <li>Troubleshooting guide</li>
            <li>2 hands-on training sessions (3 hours each)</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Best For</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Communities wanting to start rooftop/terrace gardens</li>
            <li>Neighbourhoods addressing urban heat issues</li>
            <li>Groups with identified spaces and interested residents</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Requirements</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Identified space (rooftop, terrace, or balconies)</li>
            <li>Minimum 10 interested community members</li>
            <li>Basic commitment to maintenance</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Status:</strong> Available - Can support 2-3 communities at a time</p>
        <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:contact@c4c.example.org">contact@c4c.example.org</a></p>
    </article>
</section>

